🔹 Table Types
1. Permanent Table
Default table type
Has Time Travel + Fail-safe
2. Temporary Table
CREATE TEMP TABLE temp_table AS
SELECT * FROM my_table;
Session-based
Automatically deleted
3. Transient Table
CREATE TRANSIENT TABLE trans_table AS
SELECT * FROM my_table;
No Fail-safe
Lower storage cost

